**New ****Breakfast**** Options**

- Fruit/Yogurt – Change to full fat Greek yogurt. Variations – Skyr, Natural, Cottage Cheese

- Fruit: Strawberries, raspberries, blueberries (fresh or frozen), plums, peaches

- Bananas, not every day, apple, Rhubarb

- Tinned fruit – pears, peaches, prunes, plums, apricots

- Eggs – boiled, scrambled, fired, omelette, frittata/tortilla

- With smoked salmon

- Spinach

- Mushrooms

- Peppers

- shakshuka

- Continental

- Cured meat - Prosciutto / Parma ham / Serrano / Bresaola

- Cheese – Good cheddar, parmesan, Halloumi, Feta, My regular favourites

- Cucumber, Tomato, olives, other salad

- Full English – eggs, bacon, sausage, mushroom, tomato

- Steak and eggs

- Mediterranean

- hard-boiled eggs, cucumber, tomato, olives, feta, hummus, pitta, perhaps a small piece of smoked fish, a handful of fresh herbs (parsley, mint, dill)

- Cottage Cheese

- Savoury with salad type ingredients

- Sweet – yogurt replacement

- Breakfast Bowl

- Avocado, smoked salmon, soft egg, cucumber bowl

- Mushroom and spinach bowl

- Last night's leftovers bowl

- Smoked Haddock